content.source:
Hmmm… very interesting. Here are my stats as of, well, now.

* **Internet Explorer 6.0** - 39%
* **Gecko browsers** - 22%
* **Internet Explorer 5.x (Win & Mac)** - 19%
* **Crawlers/Search Engines** - 12%
* **Netscape 4.x** - 3%
* **Safari** - 3%
* **Opera 7.x** - 2%

Gecko browsers are gaining on IE 6.0 here at Skyzyx.com. It’s good to know.
